snippet.title: Pixel Puzzle Makeout League - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Solve pixel puzzles, date superheroes, and save the day! Dating sim meets puzzle game in this romantic comedy adventure.

Coming 10/30 to Nintendo Switch and PC/Mac:
https://picross.love

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/cXyRCtc
Follow Rude Ghost on Twitter: https://twitter.com/RudeGhostGames

Developed by Rude Ghost. Published by Skymap Games.
